WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.250
When facing a persistent leadership challenge, consider the See-Think-Wonder routine.

00:00:04.250 --> 00:00:08.500
First, observe what is objectively happening in the organization. Second,

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:12.750
analyze what the root cause might be. Third, wonder about

00:00:12.750 --> 00:00:17.000
potential solutions. This sequence is an active thinking scaffold designed

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.250
to cultivate sensitivity, inclination, and the ability to deploy good

00:00:21.250 --> 00:00:25.500
thinking spontaneously when under pressure. Reflect on how applying this

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:29.750
sequence might change the outcome of a current challenge, rather

00:00:29.750 --> 00:00:34.000
than reacting impulsively.
